Docs.summary: Contains compiler-generated types that are not intended to be used directly from your code.

remarks.format: ## Remarks Do not use or include this namespace. The purpose of this namespace is a container for the <xref:XamlGeneratedNamespace.GeneratedInternalTypeHelper> class <xref:XamlGeneratedNamespace.GeneratedInternalTypeHelper> is an internal helper that the XAML markup compiler produces for XAML type resolution against assemblies.
